---
title: Smart Pork Crunch Salad with Peanuts and Edamame
description: Crunchy coleslaw mix and crisp sweet bell peppers add fun to every bite of this salad. Soy and mirin combine in a sweet, sticky glaze that dresses lean ground pork and protein-rich edamame.
